Interface IFileStructureLoader

All Superinterfaces:
IStructureLoader
All Known Implementing Classes:
CifStructureLoader, FastaStructureLoader, PdbStructureLoader, TestStructureLoader
public interface IFileStructureLoader
extends IStructureLoader

Defines the standard interface for classes which know how to load a Structure from a file or url object.
